<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-10-09T15:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-10-09T15:00:00-05:00" n="427" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d427">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 763.72111/5654a</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Diplomatic Representatives in Argentina, Chile,
                                    Colombia, Ecuador, Paraguay, Peru, and Venezuela</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Circular telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-10-09T15:00:00-05:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">October 9, 1917, 3 p.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Inform Department by cable what restrictions, if any, are imposed by
                            Government of country to which you are accredited upon entrance into its
                            ports of armed American merchantmen engaged in commerce.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <persName corresp="frus1917Supp02v01#p_LR1">
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Lansing</hi>
                                </persName>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>